content.rendered:
Reading Time: < 1 minute

Some much-needed good news for Britney Spears: It’s her birthday y’all!!!!

The pop superstar, currently battling rumors that boyfriend Jason Trawick attacked her, turns 29 today. We hope that gives Brit 29 reasons to smile.

It looks like Jason Alexander’s story is fake (thank goodness), but after all she’s gone through, we were so worried. Our girl deserves only the best!

The birthday girl with embattled boyfriend Jason Trawick.

She’s brought us so much joy, from musical and gossip standpoints. We’re thrilled to wish the pride of Kentwood the happiest of birthdays today.

Have a great 29th, sweetie, and know that BS Nation has your back 150 percent. Click to enlarge our tribute in Britney Spears pictures below!
